  "title": "animationFrameScheduler",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L37-L36\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs/tree/8.0.0-alpha.14/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts#L37-L36\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index\", \"name\": \"rxjs/index\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\", \"name\": \"animationFrameScheduler\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/index\">rxjs/index</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"animationframescheduler\">animationFrameScheduler<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#animationframescheduler\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p>Animation Frame Scheduler</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a>: AnimationFrameScheduler;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p><span class=\"informal\">Perform task when <code>window.requestAnimationFrame</code> would fire</span></p>\n<p>When <code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a></code> scheduler is used with delay, it will fall back to <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a>\nscheduler behaviour.</p>\n<p>Without delay, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a></code> scheduler can be used to create smooth browser animations.\nIt makes sure scheduled task will happen just before next browser content repaint,\nthus performing animations as efficiently as possible.</p>\n<h2 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Schedule div height animation</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n// html: &#x3C;div style=\"background: #0ff;\">&#x3C;/div>\nimport { <a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a> } from 'rxjs';\n\nconst div = document.querySelector('div');\n\nanimationFrameScheduler.schedule(function(height) {\n  div.style.height = height + \"px\";\n\n  this.schedule(height + 1);  // `this` references currently executing Action,\n                              // which we reschedule with new state\n}, 0, 0);\n\n// You will see a div element growing in height\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/index\n - api/index/function/observeOn\n - api/operators/observeOn\n - guide/scheduler\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#animationframescheduler\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#description\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#example\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L37-L36\n - https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs/tree/8.0.0-alpha.14/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts#L37-L36\n-->"
